snippet.title: Scrapyard Dog - Atari 7800
snippet.description:
EN: Scrapyard Dog, originally released for the Atari 7800, starts with Louie's dog Scraps being kidnapped by Mr. Big, who has driven off with Scraps and unleashed (get it?!) a band of thugs to stop Louie. Louie must dodge the thug's attacks while avoiding other enemies, hopping over obstacles, darting under bird droppings, and collecting cans and money.

Musique d'intro par Mnargl - http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/550444
Design et montage: Phoenix1291
Déscription vidéo: http://www.giantbomb.com/scrapyard-dog/3030-2293/
